120
00:09:48,140 --> 00:09:50,660
I came because I heard you were discharged.

121
00:09:51,680 --> 00:09:52,840
Oh, yes.

122
00:09:53,370 --> 00:09:53,910
Come in.

123
00:09:56,890 --> 00:10:01,580
Gosh, this place is totally different. It's so clean.

124
00:10:02,450 --> 00:10:04,410
This is beef bone soup.

125
00:10:04,490 --> 00:10:08,230
This is the best for bones. Eat well.

126
00:10:09,320 --> 00:10:10,910
