128
00:10:13,310 --> 00:10:15,190
We're neighbors. It's nothing.

129
00:10:15,220 --> 00:10:17,230
Just say thank you and take it.

130
00:10:17,270 --> 00:10:17,910
Okay?

131
00:10:18,030 --> 00:10:19,490
Thank you.

132
00:10:22,210 --> 00:10:24,300
