133
00:10:24,550 --> 00:10:24,800
Yes.

134
00:10:32,660 --> 00:10:32,980
Oh...

135
00:10:33,990 --> 00:10:34,890
H-hello.

136
00:10:35,220 --> 00:10:36,190
