137
00:10:36,620 --> 00:10:37,310
Are you okay?

138
00:10:38,150 --> 00:10:39,990
I'm fine.

139
00:10:40,160 --> 00:10:42,220
Eat up.

140
00:10:44,160 --> 00:10:44,910
Thank you.

141
