160
00:12:14,200 --> 00:12:16,510
But he suddenly rushed over.

161
00:12:17,110 --> 00:12:19,110
I was shocked and overturned it.

162
00:12:20,690 --> 00:12:23,880
The dough kept getting burnt so I made it for the whole day.

163
00:12:24,900 --> 00:12:26,750
I really wanted to give it to you.

164
00:12:27,820 --> 00:12:29,800
It was delicious too.

165
00:12:41,330 --> 00:12:42,150
It's delicious.

166
00:12:48,290 --> 00:12:49,170
What's with that bag?

167
00:12:51,550 --> 00:12:52,920
Well...

168
00:12:53,420 --> 00:12:56,350
