You're the patient.

203
00:16:34,820 --> 00:16:35,760
You're a guest.

204
00:16:40,910 --> 00:16:41,980
I'm really fine.

205
00:16:41,980 --> 00:16:43,610
I won't move anymore.

206
00:16:47,380 --> 00:16:48,520
I'm going to sleep here.

207
00:16:48,850 --> 00:16:50,230
It's up to you if you want to go up and sleep.

208
00:16:51,450 --> 00:16:52,410
Why?

209
00:17:07,680 --> 00:17:08,770
Should I turn this off?

210
00:17:10,470 --> 00:17:10,990
No.

211
00:17:13,540 --> 00:17:14,930
I heard it helps with sleep,

212
00:17:15,200 --> 00:17:16,560
so I bought it online.

213
00:17:16,880 --> 00:17:17,540
Let's sleep.

214
00:17:30,920 --> 00:17:32,090
Why do you keep doing this?

215
00:17:33,340 --> 00:17:34,750
Why do you keep...

216
00:17:36,500 --> 00:17:37,230
Yechan.

217
00:17:38,110 --> 00:17:39,120
Are you okay?

218
00:17:41,910 --> 00:17:42,270
Ah.

219
00:17:43,210 --> 00:17:44,000
That's when it started.

220
00:17:46,410 --> 00:17:49,460
Because of that accident... No matter how much I think about it, I must be really severely hurt.

221
00:17:50,150 --> 00:17:50,960
No.

222
00:17:51,530 --> 00:17:54,450
The X-ray showed no fractures.

223
00:17:54,910 --> 00:17:57,090
No, but after the accident,

224
00:17:57,310 --> 00:17:58,690
my chest has been hurting.

225
00:18:00,880 --> 00:18:03,880
Your blood pressure is normal.

226
00:18:04,480 --> 00:18:06,670
There's nothing unusual.

227
00:18:08,810 --> 00:18:11,700
I heard that if the heart beats fast, it could be arrhythmia.

228
00:18:13,680 --> 00:18:14,280
It's not.

229
00:18:15,650 --> 00:18:16,460
Then...

230
00:18:17,210 --> 00:18:18,890
I don't smoke or drink.

231
00:18:19,180 --> 00:18:22,540
