232
00:18:24,520 --> 00:18:25,210
No.

233
00:18:27,260 --> 00:18:29,400
I've been picking random things and eating them.

234
00:18:29,490 --> 00:18:31,850
Could it be a parasite worm that eats up hearts?

235
00:18:33,560 --> 00:18:34,830
Heart... No.

236
00:18:37,640 --> 00:18:38,130
Really?

237
00:18:40,450 --> 00:18:41,400
Then why is this happening?

238
00:18:47,510 --> 00:18:47,890
Chan.

239
00:18:48,970 --> 00:18:50,290
That's not an illness.

240
00:18:50,560 --> 00:18:51,080
Then what is it?

241
00:18:51,300 --> 00:18:51,990
It's love.

242
00:18:52,730 --> 00:18:53,280
Love.

243
00:18:54,300 --> 00:18:54,930
Huh?

244
00:18:55,560 --> 00:18:56,370
Love.

245
00:18:56,800 --> 00:18:59,500
Chan you like that person now.

246
00:19:00,090 --> 00:19:02,140
No way.

247
00:19:02,150 --> 00:19:04,240
I haven't known him for long.

248
00:19:04,250 --> 00:19:04,870
Hey man.

249
00:19:05,350 --> 00:19:07,450
Time doesn't matter in love.

250
00:19:08,370 --> 00:19:09,600
Feeling's what's important.

251
00:19:10,850 --> 00:19:11,510
Feeling?

252
00:19:12,680 --> 00:19:13,540
You said your heart beats fast

253
00:19:14,480 --> 00:19:15,470
when you see him, right?

254
00:19:16,990 --> 00:19:17,960
You get nervous too.

255
00:19:18,740 --> 00:19:20,250
It's not an illness, there's only one answer.

256
00:19:20,820 --> 00:19:22,130
You like Chief Baek's grandson, right?

257
00:19:22,630 --> 00:19:23,880
I like him?

258
00:19:24,200 --> 00:19:24,640
But...

259
00:19:25,350 --> 00:19:26,480
