260
00:19:29,410 --> 00:19:30,140
Well...

261
00:19:30,760 --> 00:19:32,000
I'm not sure.

262
00:19:32,480 --> 00:19:33,700
Then let's start with that.

263
00:19:33,920 --> 00:19:36,080
