272
00:19:57,500 --> 00:19:58,510
Ask him, Chan.

273
00:19:58,920 --> 00:19:59,710
Go! Go!

274
00:20:02,860 --> 00:20:03,490
How can I

275
00:20:04,480 --> 00:20:05,790
ask that question?

276
00:20:07,320 --> 00:20:09,300
If he's seeing anyone...

277
00:20:13,000 --> 00:20:13,790
Well...

278
00:20:26,510 --> 00:20:27,340
Bro!

279
00:20:31,440 --> 00:20:32,850
Bro!

280
00:20:36,440 --> 00:20:37,390
Bro...

281
00:20:38,850 --> 00:20:39,810
I'm here.

282
00:20:41,520 --> 00:20:43,050
You reek of alcohol.

283
00:20:43,850 --> 00:20:46,480
Why did you drink so much?

284
00:20:47,100 --> 00:20:48,060
Just...

285
00:20:49,520 --> 00:20:50,040
Just one glass?

286
00:20:50,810 --> 00:20:51,750
It doesn't look like it.

287
00:20:54,120 --> 00:20:55,510
I drank three bottles.

288
00:20:55,610 --> 00:20:56,810
Rice wine.

289
